JOHANNESBURG - Nigerian superstar Runtown is a firm believer in giving back and supporting the less fortunate.The 'Mad Over You' hitmaker was in Johannesburg recently, for a club tour and to spread awareness about his new ambassadorship in the fight to end the trafficking of girls.His very own Runtown Foundation, that aims to empower the African child, has made strides in spreading awareness of this plight across the continent.The charming, award-winning muso sat down with eNCA's Mbali Langa, to elaborate on his music career and missions of good will.eNCA